      <title>美国数千座水坝可能未做好应对极端降雨的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2438122-thousands-of-us-dams-may-be-unprepared-for-extreme-rain/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
